ue-ewing-taylor.jpg', '0', 'attachment', 'image/jpeg', '0'), ('463', '5', '2013-07-31 05:18:39', '2013-07-31 05:18:39', '', 'jay-arnone', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'open', '', 'jay-arnone-2', '', '', '2013-07-31 05:18:39', '2013-07-31 05:18:39', '', '0', 'http://m.nevadaclimatechange.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/jay-arnone.jpg', '0', 'attachment', 'image/jpeg', '0'), ('464', '5', '2013-07-31 05:18:41', '2013-07-31 05:18:41', '', 'john-farley', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'open', '', 'john-farley-2', '', '', '2013-07-31 05:18:41', '2013-07-31 05:18:41', '', '0', 'http://m.nevadaclimatechange.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/john-farley.jpg', '0', 'attachment', 'image/jpeg', '0'), ('465', '5', '2013-07-31 05:18:43', '2013-07-31 05:18:43', '', 'john-mejia', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'open', '', 'john-mejia-2', '', '', '2013-07-31 05:18:43', '2013-07-31 05:18:43', '', '0', 'http://m.nevadaclimatechange.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/john-mejia.jpg', '0', 'attachment', 'image/jpeg', '0'), ('466', '5', '2013-07-31 05:18:45', '2013-07-31 05:18:45', '', 'laurel-saito', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'open', '', 'laurel-saito-2', '', '', '2013-07-31 05:18:45', '2013-07-31 05:18:45', '', '0', 'http://m.nevadaclimatechange.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/laurel-saito.jpg', '0', 'attachment', 'image/jpeg', '0'), ('467', '5', '2013-07-31 05:18:47', '2013-07-31 05:18:47', '', 'lisa-wable', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'open', '', 'lisa-wable-2', '', '', '2013-07-31 05:18:47', '2013-07-31 05:18:47', '', '0', 'http://m.nevadaclimatechange.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/lisa-wable.jpg', '0', 'attachment', 'image/jpeg', '0'), ('509', '5', '2013-07-26 07:02:36', '2013-07-26 07:02:36', 'View data from the NCCP system directly on your mobile.  Filter sensors based on property, sensor site or type, then pick and choose from the matching list and graph or view data points from up to 5 sensors at a time.', 'Data', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'open', '', '169-revision-7', '', '', '2013-07-26 07:02:36', '2013-07-26 07:02:36', '', '169', 'http://m.nevadaclimatechange.com/169-revision-7/', '0', 'revision', '', '0'), ('397', '5', '2013-07-29 01:05:56', '2013-07-29 01:05:56', 'The Nevada Climate Change Project is dedicated to collaboration and public education. Questions regarding collaborative efforts, members, developed technologies, climate research, and general comments or inquiries are always welcome. Contact us using the form below, or if preferred, using one of the specific addresses below.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nPlease direct your inquiries or comments to:\r\n<ul id=\"EmailList\">\r\n	<li><a href=\"mailto:Gayle.Dana@dri.edu\">Gayle Dana</a> (Project Principal Investigator)</li>\r\n	<li><a href=\"mailto:Nick.Lancaster@dri.edu\">Nick Lancaster</a> (Project Co-Principal Investigator)</li>\r\n	<li><a href=\"mailto:Lynn.Fenstermaker@dri.edu\">Lynn Fenstermaker</a> (Science/Research, Transects)</li>\r\n	<li><a href=\"mailto:Jay.Arnone@dri.edu\">Jay Arnone</a> (Science/Research, Transects)</li>\r\n	<li><a href=\"mailto:dascalus@cse.unr.edu\">Sergiu Dascalu</a> (Cyberinfrastructure)</li>\r\n	<li><a href=\"mailto:mcmahon@cse.unr.edu\">Michael J. McMahon Jr.</a> (Cyberinfrastructure, Website, Database, General Information)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nAdditional contact information by individual can be found on the <a title=\"Collaborators and other persons involved with the Nevada Climate Change Project.\" href=\"http://sensor.nevada.edu/NCCP/People/Default.aspx\">People page (main site)</a>.', 'Contact', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'open', '', '21-revision-6', '', '', '2013-07-29 01:05:56', '2013-07-29 01:05:56', '', '21', 'http://m.nevadaclimatechange.com/21-revision-6/', '0', 'revision', '', '0'), ('508', '5', '2013-08-01 07:59:43', '2013-08-01 07:59:43', 'The Nevada Climate Change Project is dedicated to collaboration and public education. Questions regarding collaborative efforts, members, developed technologies, climate research, and general comments or inquiries are always welcome. Contact us using the form below, or if preferred, using one of the specific addresses below.\r\n\r\n<!--cforms name=\"Contact\"-->\r\n\r\nPlease direct your inquiries or comments to:\r\n<ul id=\"EmailList\">\r\n	<li><a href=\"mailto:Gayle.Dana@dri.edu\">Gayle Dana</a> (Project Principal Investigator)</li>\r\n	<li><a href=\"mailto:Nick.Lancaster@dri.edu\">Nick Lancaster</a> (Project Co-Principal Investigator)</li>\r\n	<li><a href=\"mailto:Lynn.Fenstermaker@dri.edu\">Lynn Fenstermaker</a> (Science/Research, Transects)</li>\r\n	<li><a href=\"mailto:Jay.Arnone@dri.edu\">Jay Arnone</a> (Science/Research, Transects)</li>\r\n	<li><a href=\"mailto:dascalus@cse.unr.edu\">Sergiu Dascalu</a> (Cyberinfrastructure)</li>\r\n	<li><a href=\"mailto:mcmahon@cse.unr.edu\">Michael J. McMahon Jr.</a> (Cyberinfrastructure, Website, Database, General Information)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nAdditional contact information by individual can be found on the <a title=\"Collaborators and other persons involved with the Nevada Climate Change Project.\" href=\"/contact/people\">People page</a>.', 'Contact', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'open', '', '21-revision-8', '', '', '2013-08-01 07:59:43', '2013-08-01 07:59:43', '', '21', 'http://m.nevadaclimatechange.com/21-revision-8/', '0', 'revision', '', '0'), ('398', '5', '2013-07-26 07:02:02', '2013-07-26 07:02:02', '<h2>Project Participants</h2>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<figure><a title=\"The Nevada System of Higher Education.\" href=\"http://www.nevada.edu\" target=\"_blank\"><img style=\"height: 50px; width: 50px;\" title=\"The Nevada System of Higher Education.\" alt=\"NSHE\" src=\"http://sensor.nevada.edu/NCCP/images/Institution%20logos/NSHE.svg\" /></a>\r\n<figcaption><a title=\"The Nevada System of Higher Education.\" href=\"http://www.nevada.edu\" target=\"_blank\">Nevada System of Higher Education</a></figcaption></figure><figure><a title=\"Great Basin College.\" href=\"http://www.gbcnv.edu/\" target=\"_blank\"><img style=\"height: 50px; width: 50px;\" title=\"Great Basin College.\" alt=\"GBC\" src=\"http://sensor.nevada.edu/NCCP/images/Institution%20logos/GBC.svg\" /></a>\r\n<figcaption><a title=\"Great Basin College.\" href=\"http://www.gbcnv.edu/\" target=\"_blank\">Great Basin College</a></figcaption></figure><figure><a title=\"The Desert Research Institute.\" href=\"http://www.dri.edu\" target=\"_blank\"><img style=\"height: 50px; width: 50px;\" title=\"The Desert Research Institute.\" alt=\"DRI\" src=\"http://sensor.nevada.edu/NCCP/images/Institution%20logos/DRI.svg\" /></a>\r\n<figcaption><a title=\"The Desert Research Institute.\" href=\"http://www.dri.edu\" target=\"_blank\">Desert Research Institute</a></figcaption></figure><figure><a title=\"Nevada State College.\" href=\"http://nsc.nevada.edu\" target=\"_blank\"><img style=\"height: 50px; width: 50px;\" title=\"Nevada State College.\" alt=\"NSC\" src=\"http://sensor.nevada.edu/NCCP/images/Institution%20logos/NSC.svg\" /></a>\r\n<figcaption><a title=\"Nevada State College.\" href=\"http://nsc.nevada.edu\" target=\"_blank\">Nevada State College</a></figcaption></figure><figure><a title=\"The University of Nevada, Las Vegas.\" href=\"http://www.unlv.edu\" target=\"_blank\"><img style=\"height: 50px; width: 50px;\" title=\"The University of Nevada, Las Vegas.\" alt=\"UNLV\" src=\"http://sensor.nevada.edu/NCCP/images/Institution%20logos/UNLV.svg\" /></a>\r\n<figcaption><a title=\"The University of Nevada, Las Vegas.\" href=\"http://www.unlv.edu\" target=\"_blank\">University of Nevada, Las Vegas</a></figcaption></figure><figure><a title=\"Truckee Meadows Community College.\" href=\"http://www.tmcc.edu/\" target=\"_blank\"><img style=\"height: 50px; width: 50px;\" title=\"Truckee Meadows Community College.\" alt=\"TMCC\" src=\"http://sensor.nevada.edu/NCCP/images/Institution%20logos/TMCC.svg\" /></a>\r\n<figcaption><a title=\"Truckee Meadows Community College.\" href=\"http://www.tmcc.edu/\" target=\"_blank\">Truckee Meadows Community College</a></figcaption></figure><figure><a title=\"The University of Nevada, Reno.\" href=\"http://www.unr.edu\" target=\"_blank\"><img style=\"height: 50px; width: 50px;\" title=\"The University of Nevada, Reno.\" alt=\"NSHE\" src=\"http://sensor.nevada.edu/NCCP/images/Institution%20logos/UNR.svg\" /></a>\r\n<figcaption><a title=\"The University of Nevada, Reno.\" href=\"http://www.unr.edu\" target=\"_blank\">University of Nevada, Reno</a></figcaption></figure><figure><a title=\"Western Nevada College.\" href=\"http://www.wnc.edu/\" target=\"_blank\"><img style=\"height: 50px; width: 50px;\" title=\"Western Nevada College.\" alt=\"WNC\" src=\"http://sensor.nevada.edu/NCCP/images/Institution%20logos/WNC.svg\" /></a>\r\n<figcaption><a title=\"Western Nevada College.\" href=\"http://www.wnc.edu/\" target=\"_blank\">Western Nevada College</a></figcaption></figure><figure><a title=\"College of Southern Nevada.\" href=\"http://www.csn.edu/\" target=\"_blank\"><img style=\"height: 50px; width: 50px;\" title=\"College of Southern Nevada.\" alt=\"CSN\" src=\"http://sensor.nevada.edu/NCCP/images/Institution%20logos/CSN.svg\" /></a>\r\n<figcaption><a title=\"College of Southern Nevada.\" href=\"http://www.csn.edu/\" target=\"_blank\">College of Southern Nevada</a></figcaption></figure>', 'People', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'open', '', '17-revision-7', '', '', '2013-07-26 07:02:02', '2013-07-26 07:02:02', '', '17', 'http://m.nevadaclimatechange.com/17-revision-7/', '0', 'revision', '', '0'), ('563', '5', '2013-10-01 06:05:50', '2013-10-01 06:05:50', '<h1>Welcome to the NCCP</h1>\r\nWelcome to the Nevada Climate Change Portal. Climate data from the NCCP database can be retrieved, graphed or downloaded directly to your phone or tablet.\r\n<h3><a title=\"Get Data\" href=\"http://m.nevadaclimatechange.com/get-data/\">Get Data</a></h3>\r\nYou can also access our educational resources:\r\n<h3><a title=\"Education\" href=\"http://m.nevadaclimatechange.com/education/\">Activities</a></h3>\r\n<h3><a title=\"Resources\" href=\"http://m.nevadaclimatechange.com/education/science-activities/\">Resources</a></h3>\r\nOr learn more about the NCCP project, the SENSOR network or the research sites:\r\n<h3><a title=\"The Project\" href=\"http://m.nevadaclimatechange.com/the-project/\">Learn About the Project</a></h3>', 'Home', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'open', '', '4-revision-v1', '', '', '2013-10-01 06:05:50', '2013-10-01 06:05:50', '', '4', 'http://m.nevadaclimatechange.com/4-revision-v1/', '0', 'revision', '', '0'), ('283', '5', '2013-04-30 04:19:30', '2013-04-30 04:19:30', '<h2>Welcome to NCCP Mobile</h2>\r\nThis site provides mobile access to sensor data from the Nevada Climate Change Portal (NCCP).  Data from the NCCP database can be retrieved, graphed or downloaded directly to your phone or tablet.\r\n<h3><a title=\"Get Data\" href=\"http://nccp.monterey-j.com/get-data/\">Get Data</a></h3>\r\n<svg class=\"graph random\"></svg>\r\nYou can also learn more about the project or access educational resources.\r\n<h3><a title=\"Resources\" href=\"http://nccp.monterey-j.com/resources/\">Resources</a></h3>\r\n<h3><a title=\"The Project\" href=\"http://nccp.monterey-j.com/the-project/\">Learn About the Project</a></h3>\r\n<h3><a title=\"Education\" href=\"http://nccp.monterey-j.com/resources/education/\">Activities</a></h3>\r\nFinally, you can view the status of the main portal as well as the Data API.\r\n<h3><a title=\"Status\" href=\"http://nccp.monterey-j.com/status/\">Status</a></h3>\r\nSwipe the screen left and right to navigate between subpages.', 'Home', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'open', '', '4-revision-v1', '', '', '2013-04-30 04:19:30', '2013-04-30 04:19:30', '', '4', 'http://nccp.monterey-j.com/4-revision-19/', '0', 'revision', '', '0'), ('408', '5', '2013-07-29 01:52:09', '2013-07-29 01:52:09', '', 'Douglas Boyle', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'douglas-boyle', '', '', '2013-07-31 05:37:47', '2013-07-31 05:37:47', '', '0', 'http://m.nevadaclimatechange.com/?post_type=person&#03