=\"_blank\">Great Basin College</a></figcaption></figure><figure><a title=\"The Desert Research Institute.\" href=\"http://www.dri.edu\" target=\"_blank\"><img style=\"height: 50px; width: 50px;\" title=\"The Desert Research Institute.\" alt=\"DRI\" src=\"http://sensor.nevada.edu/NCCP/images/Institution%20logos/DRI.svg\" /></a> <figcaption><a title=\"The Desert Research Institute.\" href=\"http://www.dri.edu\" target=\"_blank\">Desert Research Institute</a></figcaption></figure><figure><a title=\"Nevada State College.\" href=\"http://nsc.nevada.edu\" target=\"_blank\"><img style=\"height: 50px; width: 50px;\" title=\"Nevada State College.\" alt=\"NSC\" src=\"http://sensor.nevada.edu/NCCP/images/Institution%20logos/NSC.svg\" /></a> <figcaption><a title=\"Nevada State College.\" href=\"http://nsc.nevada.edu\" target=\"_blank\">Nevada State College</a></figcaption></figure><figure><a title=\"The University of Nevada, Las Vegas.\" href=\"http://www.unlv.edu\" target=\"_blank\"><img style=\"height: 50px; width: 50px;\" title=\"The University of Nevada, Las Vegas.\" alt=\"UNLV\" src=\"http://sensor.nevada.edu/NCCP/images/Institution%20logos/UNLV.svg\" /></a> <figcaption><a title=\"The University of Nevada, Las Vegas.\" href=\"http://www.unlv.edu\" target=\"_blank\">University of Nevada, Las Vegas</a></figcaption></figure><figure><a title=\"Truckee Meadows Community College.\" href=\"http://www.tmcc.edu/\" target=\"_blank\"><img style=\"height: 50px; width: 50px;\" title=\"Truckee Meadows Community College.\" alt=\"TMCC\" src=\"http://sensor.nevada.edu/NCCP/images/Institution%20logos/TMCC.svg\" /></a> <figcaption><a title=\"Truckee Meadows Community College.\" href=\"http://www.tmcc.edu/\" target=\"_blank\">Truckee Meadows Community College</a></figcaption></figure><figure><a title=\"The University of Nevada, Reno.\" href=\"http://www.unr.edu\" target=\"_blank\"><img style=\"height: 50px; width: 50px;\" title=\"The University of Nevada, Reno.\" alt=\"NSHE\" src=\"http://sensor.nevada.edu/NCCP/images/Institution%20logos/UNR.svg\" /></a> <figcaption><a title=\"The University of Nevada, Reno.\" href=\"http://www.unr.edu\" target=\"_blank\">University of Nevada, Reno</a></figcaption></figure><figure><a title=\"Western Nevada College.\" href=\"http://www.wnc.edu/\" target=\"_blank\"><img style=\"height: 50px; width: 50px;\" title=\"Western Nevada College.\" alt=\"WNC\" src=\"http://sensor.nevada.edu/NCCP/images/Institution%20logos/WNC.svg\" /></a> <figcaption><a title=\"Western Nevada College.\" href=\"http://www.wnc.edu/\" target=\"_blank\">Western Nevada College</a></figcaption></figure><figure><a title=\"College of Southern Nevada.\" href=\"http://www.csn.edu/\" target=\"_blank\"><img style=\"height: 50px; width: 50px;\" title=\"College of Southern Nevada.\" alt=\"CSN\" src=\"http://sensor.nevada.edu/NCCP/images/Institution%20logos/CSN.svg\" /></a> <figcaption><a title=\"College of Southern Nevada.\" href=\"http://www.csn.edu/\" target=\"_blank\">College of Southern Nevada</a></figcaption></figure>', 'People', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'open', '', '17-revision-4', '', '', '2013-03-18 05:21:08', '2013-03-18 05:21:08', '', '17', 'http://nccp.monterey-j.com/17-revision-4/', '0', 'revision', '', '0'), ('365', '5', '2013-04-11 04:40:57', '2013-04-11 04:40:57', 'View data from the NCCP system directly on your mobile.  Filter sensors based on property, sensor site or type, then pick and choose from the matching list and graph or view data points from up to 5 sensors at a time.', 'Get Data', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'open', '', '169-revision-6', '', '', '2013-04-11 04:40:57', '2013-04-11 04:40:57', '', '169', 'http://m.nevadaclimatechange.com/169-revision-6/', '0', 'revision', '', '0'), ('295', '5', '2013-04-30 05:14:42', '2013-04-30 05:14:42', 'A number of educational materials and informative articles are made available that explain various aspects of the research that is conducted as a part of the project.\r\n\r\nHands-on experiments are designed for provide instructors with interactive exercises that enhance student understanding of the environment and research. Below are links for each age group. (Click on the age group to expand the section.)\r\n<h3>Elementary School</h3>\r\n<a href=\"http://nccp.monterey-j.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/04/Air-Pollution-Experiment.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">Air Pollution Experiment</a>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://nccp.monterey-j.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/04/Carbon-Cycle-Activity.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">Carbon Cycle Activity</a>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://nccp.monterey-j.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/04/Conservation-v-Efficiency.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">Conservation v Efficiency</a>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://nccp.monterey-j.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/04/Energy-Sources-Game.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">Energy Sources Game</a>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://nccp.monterey-j.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/04/Greenhouse-Gas-Modeling-Experiment.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">Greenhouse Gas Modeling Experiment</a>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://nccp.monterey-j.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/04/Recycled-Art-Activities.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">Recycled Art Activities</a>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://nccp.monterey-j.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/04/Recycled-Paper-Activity.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">Recycled Paper Activity</a>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://nccp.monterey-j.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/04/Science-Fair-Activity.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">Science Fair Activity</a>\r\n<h3>Middle School</h3>\r\n<a href=\"http://nccp.monterey-j.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/04/Air-Temp-and-RH-Investigation.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">Air Temp and RH Investigation</a>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://nccp.monterey-j.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/04/Atmospheric-Anemometer-Experiment.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">Atmospheric Anemometer Experiment </a>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://nccp.monterey-j.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/04/Atmospheric-Barometer-Experiment.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">Atmospheric Barometer Experiment</a>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://nccp.monterey-j.com/wp-content/uploads/